        ],
        "content": [
            "奈迪犹意在赋予全人类龙化之力。\\n塞西娅和伊莉雅则试图\\n阻止这一危险的计划。\\n此时法尔艾斯和贝维特现身，\\n企图用黑暗魔力操纵圣域龙。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "圣树 树冠",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "奈迪犹……我不会让你\\n与巴哈姆特缔结契约的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "塞西娅！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "她是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（如果伊莉雅所言属实，\\n就得在这里阻止奈迪犹才行！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "唔！\\n你为什么，会在这里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗨，塞西娅，好久不见。\\n有1000年了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "没想到你还活着……\\n毕竟，你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错。1000年前，\\n我和莫尔提斯封印魔神时\\n投身于异界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "虽然过程一言难尽，\\n但如你所见，我活得好好的。\\n莫尔提斯也没事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不过现在暂时没空\\n为重逢而高兴，\\n得阻止奈迪犹才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "什么意思？你为什么\\n会知道奈迪犹的事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这个我们之后再说，\\n总之现在时间紧迫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "能阻止奈迪犹的\\n就只有你了，塞西娅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "只有我？\\n这话是什么意思……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "为何要阻止我？\\n你都知道些什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我听她说了\\n你想要干什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "那身装束……我懂了。\\n虽然不知道你是谁，\\n不过你应该来自过去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错。我叫伊莉雅，\\n来自1000年前。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "1000年前！？\\n而且还叫伊莉雅……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我改日再好好自我介绍一番。\\n现在当务之急是你，奈迪犹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你对大家还有所隐瞒，\\n对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你想得到晓之圣片，\\n完成和巴哈姆特的契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "然后……赋予全人类\\n龙化之力，对不对？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "让全人类龙化！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那种事……\\n真的可以实现吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "只要拥有与巴哈姆特的完整契约，\\n大多数事情都可以实现。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不过让我不可思议的是\\n他偏偏想用那力量做这种事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "强者才有选择的特权。\\n这个世界一直都是这样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "弱者甚至连选择的余地都没有……\\n就像过去的我一样！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "若能把由阿尔贝里亚王室\\n独占的龙化之力赋予人类——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "人类能获得的不止是力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "而是一对自由的羽翼。\\n不必受他人的强迫，\\n可以随心所欲自由选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这就是我的目的，\\n也是人类本应走上的正轨。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你的做法有一个漏洞。\\n对此避而不谈，又谈何正轨！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "奈迪犹的做法有漏洞？\\n什么漏洞……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "继承龙之血的天选之族\\n都要通过选龙试炼\\n才能获得龙化之力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "试炼能考验并判断\\n挑战者的身心能否承受龙化。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "在这种机制中，\\n只有具备龙化条件的人\\n才能获得这份强大的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "要是这种力量普及，\\n一定会不断出现\\n无法承受龙化的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "无法承受的话……\\n会怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "一旦龙化就会被力量所吞噬，\\n无法保持人类的外形。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "最终沦为\\n既非人亦非龙之物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "噫……做这么过分的事\\n可不行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "嘴上说是为了弱者！\\n但这样一来，\\n弱者哪还有自由啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "最后不还得死吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但也会有获得力量\\n从而得到救赎的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "那到头来不也只是一些\\n被龙化之力选中的强者吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没错！那就是你期望的世界吗！？\\n就算不用这种强硬的手段，\\n应该也有其它方法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "那你拯救得了这个世界吗？\\n拯救得了那些一味被欺压的\\n弱小民众吗？何时救，怎么救？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "为了实现理想，牺牲在所难免。\\n华而不实的想法救不了任何人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "在我看来，你那冠冕堂皇的正义\\n没有觉悟也没有理想支撑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "不过是一个空架子……\\n一副躯壳罢了。\\n就和你本人一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "一副躯壳……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "哥哥，危险！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "圣域龙！？刚才不是\\n已经打倒这家伙了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "这是黑暗魔力！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "他看起来很痛苦……这是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯哥哥\\n和贝维特哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我得感谢你呢，\\n尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "多亏了你们，\\n我似乎能轻而易举地\\n让圣域龙成为手里的棋子了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "就连圣域龙\\n也要用黑暗魔力操纵吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "毕竟没有比圣域龙\\n更值得操纵的龙了。\\n动手吧，贝维特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "嗯，虽然可能有些棘手，\\n但是我会努力的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_21_06_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
